Insurance Release Notes

Manage Claims and Policies Effectively with Insurance Claims and Policy Analytics.
Use the Insurance Claims and Policy Analytics app to get actionable insights into claims management and policy administration.

Provide Users More Access with Vlocity Insurance Permission Set Licenses.
Permission set licenses extend the functionality of user licenses. With permission set licenses, you can assign more permissions to users than what their user license supports.

Create Inbound Quote from An External System.
Use InsQuoteService:createUpdateQuoteFromExternal service to create a quote or update an existing quote with new information through an inbound API call from an external policy admin system.

Data Model Updates for Vlocity Insurance Winter '22.
This section provides a list of new data model objects and enhanced data model objects for this release.

Insurance Winter '22 Minor Releases, Fixes, and Known Issues.
This PDF provides details about the contents of this release. It also has package links for the minor releases that we add periodically.

Vlocity Insurance Application Suite Winter '22 Minor Release 234.1.
This section describes key fixes and enhancements for the Vlocity Insurance Application Suite in this minor release.
title: Vlocity Insurance Winter '22 Release Notes
